In order to activate automatic reloader so that whenever we edit off a file and hit save, it is 
going to reload our server it also anable debug mode on the flask application

if __name__ == "__main__":
    app.run()

in piece of code above app.run() should be 

if __name__ == "__main__":
    app.run(debug=True)
